description:
We continue our kick-offs around the world! Now it’s your turn Israeli Field, Middle East and North Africa Union, Euro-Asia Division, Southern Africa Indian Ocean Division, Trans-European Division, West-Central Africa Division, Inter-European Division, and East-Central Africa Division. Tune in to see what we have in store for all of you to get you prepared for your Global Youth Day projects! Don’t forget to use the hashtag #GYD21 to show us all the ways you are Reaching Out.


*GYD is using the media with permission of “The Chosen” a crowd-funded media project. 
“The Chosen” is the first-ever multi-season series based on the true stories of the gospels of Jesus Christ.  Make sure to visit their website at https://studios.vidangel.com, and check out their app https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-chosen/id1473663873 and https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vidangel.thechosen*
